## ğŸ”‘ Real-World Example
Imagine youâ€™re deploying a **microservices application**:
- A CI/CD pipeline automatically builds Docker images for each service.  
- Images are pushed to a registry.  
- Kubernetes (or Docker Swarm) automatically deploys and scales containers.  
- Monitoring tools (Prometheus, Grafana) automate alerts if a container crashes.  

